And anyway, for what it's worth,

1345
01:18:57.470 --> 01:18:58.670
I'm grading you on the effort,

1346
01:18:58.670 --> 01:19:00.420
Not the result.

1347
01:19:05.100 --> 01:19:07.430
I don't care about the grade.

1348
01:19:21.630 --> 01:19:22.830
I just wanted to see.

1349
01:19:22.850 --> 01:19:25.050
If the world
would really change.

1350
01:20:03.010 --> 01:20:05.110
Hi.

1351
01:20:05.130 --> 01:20:07.210
Hi.

1352
01:20:09.200 --> 01:20:11.220
Uh, come in.

1353
01:22:09.790 --> 01:22:11.890
