1354
01:22:11.910 --> 01:22:12.940
It worked!

1355
01:22:12.960 --> 01:22:14.690
Oh, god!

1356
01:22:16.730 --> 01:22:18.550
Eugene: Does he always
get up this early?

1357
01:22:18.570 --> 01:22:19.600
What?

1358
01:22:19.620 --> 01:22:20.970
Oh, my god, this is not good.

1359
01:22:20.990 --> 01:22:21.970
