1360
01:22:21.990 --> 01:22:23.560
It's ok!

1361
01:22:23.580 --> 01:22:25.400
Now you have to
pay it forward, too!

1362
01:22:25.420 --> 01:22:26.850
Trevor: Eugene?

1363
01:22:26.870 --> 01:22:27.880
I think you should.

1364
01:22:27.900 --> 01:22:29.970
Still call me mr. Simonet.

1365
01:22:29.990 --> 01:22:30.970
You had a sleepover, didn't you?

1366
01:22:30.990 --> 01:22:31.980
Why don't you go back to bed?

1367
01:22:32.000 --> 01:22:33.030
Why?

1368
01:22:33.050 --> 01:22:34.150
It's too early
for you to be up...

1369
01:22:34.170 --> 01:22:35.450
No, it's not early!
No, it's a Sunday!

1370
01:22:35.470 --> 01:22:36.450
It's a Sunday?

1371
01:22:36.470 --> 01:22:37.700
Yeah.

1372
01:22:37.720 --> 01:22:38.790
So stay, stay!

1373
01:22:38.810 --> 01:22:39.790
You don't understand,

1374
01:22:39.810 --> 01:22:40.790
I have a whole schedule.

1375
01:22:40.810 --> 01:22:41.910
That you don't know about.

1376
01:22:41.930 --> 01:22:43.500
All right, well,
bring everything here!

1377
01:22:43.520 --> 01:22:44.970
Would you please
take care of him?

1378
01:22:44.990 --> 01:22:46.670
I'll call you later, all right?

1379
01:22:46.690 --> 01:22:47.720
Don't be a stranger!

1380
01:22:47.740 --> 01:22:48.810
God, trevor!

1381
01:22:48.830 --> 01:22:50.110
Trevor: Do you like him?

1382
01:23:26.720 --> 01:23:28.170
Ok.

1383
01:24:12.860 --> 01:24:14.790
Hey! Hey, hey!

1384
01:24:14.810 --> 01:24:16.330
Lady, come on.

1385
01:24:16.350 --> 01:24:17.780
Go away.

1386
01:24:17.800 --> 01:24:20.430
I-I'm not gonna hurt you, lady.

1387
01:24:20.450 --> 01:24:21.840
Oh, here, take it!

1388
01:24:21.860 --> 01:24:22.900
Well, it's a nice thought,

1389
01:24:22.910 --> 01:24:24.310
