1391
01:24:26.370 --> 01:24:27.930
Hey, what are you doing?

1392
01:24:27.950 --> 01:24:30.440
I'm not gonna hurt you!

1393
01:24:30.460 --> 01:24:32.740
What are you... hey!

1394
01:24:32.760 --> 01:24:35.830
Oh, my god! Listen to me.

1395
01:24:35.850 --> 01:24:36.870
Nothing's this important!

1396
01:24:36.890 --> 01:24:39.170
Come on, come... come down here!

1397
01:24:39.190 --> 01:24:40.620
What are you doing?

1398
01:24:40.640 --> 01:24:42.990
Woman: What do
you care, anyway?

1399
01:24:43.010 --> 01:24:44.360
Because I owe somebody a favor.

1400
01:24:44.380 --> 01:24:46.370
Not me.

1401
01:24:46.390 --> 01:24:47.920
Why not you?

1402
01:24:47.940 --> 01:24:49.370
You know... heh!

1403
01:24:49.390 --> 01:24:50.880
A minute ago,

1404
01:24:50.900 --> 01:24:52.380
All I could think about.

1405
01:24:52.400 --> 01:24:55.030
Was getting my next fix,

1406
01:24:55.050 --> 01:24:58.170
And then I saw you, a-and...

1407
01:24:58.190 --> 01:24:59.590
I changed my thinking.

1408
01:24:59.610 --> 01:25:00.930
Oh, please!

1409
01:25:00.950 --> 01:25:02.260
Go away!

1410
01:25:02.280 --> 01:25:04.390
Trust me, I'm not worth it.

1411
01:25:04.410 --> 01:25:06.440
Why's that?

1412
01:25:06.460 --> 01:25:07.720
Oh, for god's sake!

1413
01:25:07.740 --> 01:25:08.780
Come on, tell me!

1414
01:25:08.800 --> 01:25:11.280
Why are you not worth it?

1415
01:25:11.300 --> 01:25:13.740
Trust me...

1416
01:25:13.760 --> 01:25:15.990
